claim.claim-text:
1. A third brake inner indicating light mainly comprising a third brake light, a projector and a receiver wherein: 
The third brake light is connected to the receiver and designed with an inner indicator at the back; 
The projector is found at the top of the bumper and connected to the receiver such that a short range electric-wave is emitted while backing a car; 
The receiver, designed with a micro-computer is found at the baggage compartment and is separately connected to the third brake light and the projector and warms the driver when receiving any reaction wave by means of letters, signals or diagrams projected in the inner indicating screen.
